Hän teki läpimurtonsa hitillään Wet Dream, joka nousi Britannian singlelistan kymmenen kärkeen ja pysyi listoilla 25 viikon ajan, vaikka BBC kielsi sen soittamisen liian provokatiivisena.
title_translated: Musician Max Romeo is dead
description_translated: Max Romeo, one of the world's most famous regga singers, died on Friday in heart complications. He was 80 years old. Jamaican regga artist Max Romeo has died at the age of 80. He died of heart complications at Jamaica on Friday, the Guardian reported. Romeo, who rose to fame in the late 1960s, was one of the most famous reggaem musicians of his time. He made his breakthrough with his hit Wet Dream, which rose to the top ten of the British singles list and stayed on the list for 25 weeks, even though the BBC denied it too provocative.
